Class MailSendRecv

java.lang.Object
grafiosch.entities.BaseID<Integer>
grafiosch.entities.MailSendRecv
@Entity public class MailSendRecv extends BaseID<Integer>
Base class for mailing system. Mail also supports M2M on GT. Attention the ID's of the role must be the same on all GT instances.
